// authService.js
var users=[{email:"user1@example.com",password:"password1"},{email:"user2@example.com",password:"password2"}];export var signUp=function signUp(email,password){var userExists=users.some(function(user){return user.email===email;});if(userExists){return{success:false,message:"User already exists"};}users.push({email:email,password:password});return{success:true,message:"User registered successfully"};};export var login=function login(email,password){var user=users.find(function(user){return user.email===email&&user.password===password;});if(user){return{success:true,message:"Login successful"};}return{success:false,message:"Invalid email or password"};};
